data.description: This ranch home in the heart of New Carlisle has almost 1400 square feet of living space! You'll love the 2 separate living spaces and natural light this home offers. All of the big items have been taken care of for you...Roof complete tear off in 2022; Plumbing, electric, furnace and A/C all updated in the last 10 years. Schedule your showing today and envision adding your personal touches to make this home yours!
